title: Ep 453 | Phil Gives Dolly Parton a Shout-Out & Jase Shares a Dating Strategy
description:
Phil commends Dolly Parton's example of staying the course and credits her spirituality for her success. Jase calls dating a ministry and shares a strategy when dating for marriage. Al reveals his favorite music of all time, and Jase recalls a particular fad that swept him up during his teens. And Al and Jase discuss the many quarrels among believers.
